## FEATURES

• **LIVE PATTERN OVERLAY** – See your spray vs ideal pattern
• **ALL WEAPONS** – Every gun with unique recoil
• **SPEED CONTROL** – Practice at 50%, 75%, or 100% speed
• **VISUAL GUIDES** – Ideal path shown as dotted line
• **STATS TRACKING** – Accuracy percentage over time
• **BURST MODE** – Practice 5, 10, or 30 round bursts
• **WALL IMPACT** – See where bullets actually land
• **NO CS2 NEEDED** – Train anywhere, anytime

